<p>how to copy this respective number on dial pad ?</p>  <pre><code>Button but = (Button) findViewById(R.id.button1);     but.setOnClickListener(new OnClickListener() {          public void onClick(View v) {             String number = "*#*#7378423#*#*";             Intent callNumber = new Intent();             callNumber.setAction(android.content.Intent.ACTION_DIAL);             callNumber.setData(Uri.parse("tel:" + number));             startActivity(callNumber);         }     } </code></pre>